org.bonitasoft.engine.identity

Enum ImportPolicy

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<ImportPolicy>
      • org.bonitasoft.engine.identity.ImportPolicy
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<ImportPolicy>

    public enum ImportPolicy
extends Enum<ImportPolicy>
    Define how to handle conflicts when an organization is imported.
    Check OrganizationAPI.importOrganization(String) and OrganizationAPI.importOrganization(String, ImportPolicy) to see the usage.
    Since:
    6.0.0
    Author:
    Baptiste Mesta
    See Also:
    OrganizationAPI

    • Enum Constant Summary

      Enum Constants 
      Enum Constant and Description
      FAIL_ON_DUPLICATES
      If an item already exists the import fail and is reverted to previous state
      IGNORE_DUPLICATES
      Existing items are kept
      MERGE_DUPLICATES
      Existing items in current organization are updated to have the values of the item in the given organization
